title: Burrito Chai
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small restaurant serving freshly made-in-house burritos, sangria, margaritas and an assortment of vegan tidbits. Vegan choices offered are sour cream, meat substitute, a rice with beans plate that includes a sampler of sauces/salads. Minimal seating. Eclectic customer base.
